detail: Initial Section 2 setup and dataset shape
All required config roots present and Section 2 constants registered.
Dataset already loaded in Section 1; recorded shape, memory footprint, and dtype counts for Section 2.
Computed baseline per-column stats (null %, unique counts, constant flags) and saved to baseline_summary.csv.
Auto-detected potential ID columns (high uniqueness, name hints) and merged with config-driven IDs into protected_columns.yaml.
Registered Section 2 nodes (2.0.x infra + 2.1–2.9 pipeline) into section2_registry.json.
Printed Section 2 execution map and wrote section2_execution_map.md for documentation.
